### 3. Get All Movies (Browse Page)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/movies

### 4. Get Single Movie Details (Movie Detail Page)
# Replace '1' with an actual ID from the list above
GET http://localhost:5000/api/movies/1

### 5. Get All Showtimes (Unfiltered)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/showtimes

### 6. Search Showtimes by Movie (e.g., Showtimes for 'Inception')
# Replace movieId=1 with a valid ID
GET http://localhost:5000/api/showtimes?movieId=1

### 7. Search Showtimes by Date
# Format: YYYY-MM-DD
GET http://localhost:5000/api/showtimes?date=2025-01-01

### 8. Search Showtimes by Movie AND Date (Specific filter)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/showtimes?movieId=1&date=2025-01-01

### 9. Get Seats for a Specific Showtime (Clicking a Showtime)
# Replace '1' with a valid showtimeId found in previous requests
GET http://localhost:5000/api/showtimes/1/seats

